headline: County prosecutors probing whether Edison should be criminally prosecuted for Eaton fire
summary: The Los Angeles County district attorney is investigating whether Southern California Edison should be criminally prosecuted for its actions in last year's devastating Eaton wildfire, which killed 19 people and left thousands of families homeless.
